This paper discusses issues related to web archiving, which involves the preservation and access of web content. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DL (Digital Libraries). The paper also discusses issues related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and web technologies (cs.WEB), which are closely related to web archiving. Additionally, the paper discusses security issues (cs.CR) related to cookies and the need for proper implementation (cs.SE).
